message.raw:
Simplified version-finding code
Made installer actually install easy_install/setuptools
Known issue: arch/lib cannot be python-installation/lib, otherwise
  setuptools and python fight over site.py
Changed global MIN_GENOMEDATA_VERSION to GENOMEDATA_VERSION. This is what
  your release.sh script should change.
